name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Press admit button in Google Meet

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It presses admit/admit all in Google Meet automatically

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It is boring to press "Admit", "Admit all" all the time when somebody wants to join your Google Meet room. This extension just does it for you.

Works with other languages, default English.
